# pyenv
.python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different system architectures,
#   and build a lock file for their platform, it may lock standard dependencies.
#   So, we include Pipfile.lock in version control, but you can choose to ignore it.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is recommended to include poetry.lock in version control.
#   poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is recommended to include pdm.lock in version control.
#   pdm.lock

